{"id":"74ed367dd43611959a619b470a288d25878f785a729581a3ec0df16a3ae880b4","item_id":"285efc24fe:9","text":"Scale T（T 缩放）"}
{"id":"8d77229be07256f7011211680353091e34811d3fc79b9709288db976e7bea50a","item_id":"285efc24fe:10","text":"特征在 T 方向上的 Frequency（频率）。"}
{"id":"79182e90c534c862c9a1371a047fc3b73fd5f5b657802cfcfd78324f778ab585","item_id":"285efc24fe:11","text":"Offset S（S 偏移）"}
{"id":"420e2a6ad4bb108b4f211a9caa314cd5860b5fc4cdb1ef929b1cde04e994b185","item_id":"285efc24fe:12","text":"相对于原点在 S 方向上的 Offset（偏移）。"}
