{"id":"e3109eb112b8b5d6dd25efb433f70bf813e165da8c7f3800a0e999d7ee918b11","item_id":"285efc24fe:15","text":"Invert T（反转 T）"}
{"id":"537f65391f4150b2b207f8f7a5f1f95452060e7b424c643ab6fccb9a529c7099","item_id":"285efc24fe:16","text":"在 T 方向翻转 manifold（流形）。"}
